<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation - StudySync</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .order-details {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .order-summary {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #27ae60;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
        }
        .social-icons {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .social-icons a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://public.blob.vercel-storage.com/eEZHAoPTOBSYGBE/studysync-logo-white-6oup3lXCOhTDkIBwTFxiVrUuF6kZgJ.png" alt="StudySync Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="order-details">
            <h2>Thank you for your order, <%= order.name %>!</h2>
            <p>We're thrilled to confirm your course purchase. Get ready to embark on an exciting learning journey!</p>
            
            <div class="order-summary">
                <h3>Order Summary</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= order._id %></li>
                    <li><strong>Course:</strong> <%= order.name %></li>
                    <li><strong>Price:</strong> $<%= order.price %></li>
                    <li><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= order.data %></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>You can access your course by clicking the button below:</p>
            <a href="https://study-sync-ten.vercel.app/my-courses" class="btn">Start Learning Now</a>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help!</p>
            <a href="mailto:hardikbhammar8040@.com" class="btn" style="background-color: #27ae60;">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 StudySync. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="https://facebook.com/studysync">Facebook</a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/studysync">Twitter</a>
                <a href="https://instagram.com/studysync">Instagram</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>